---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<footer class="bg-lastbite-darkGreen text-white pt-16 pb-8 px-8 mt-12 rounded-t-[3rem] md:rounded-t-[4rem]">
  <div class="max-w-md md:max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 md:gap-8">
    
    <div class="md:col-span-1">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-lastbite-green mb-6">
        <Icon name="solar:leaf-bold" class="w-7 h-7" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-green-50 font-body text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
        Platform digital untuk mengurangi limbah, menghemat pengeluaran, dan membangun komunitas yang lebih berkelanjutan di area Jember.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-5">Pengguna</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-green-100 text-sm">
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Dapatkan Aplikasi</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cari Diskon</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cara Membeli</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Kebijakan Refund</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-5">Mitra</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-green-100 text-sm">
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Jadi Penjual</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Panduan Penjual</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Cerita Sukses</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Login Mitra</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-5">LastBite</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-green-100 text-sm">
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Tentang LastBite</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Hubungi Kami</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Kebijakan Privasi</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-md md:max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/20 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">
    <p class="font-body text-green-200 text-xs">
      © 2026 LastBite. Hak cipta dilindungi.
    </p>
    
    <div class="flex gap-5 text-green-200">
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-label="Instagram">
        <Icon name="solar:camera-minimalistic-linear" class="w-5 h-5" />
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors" aria-label="Website">
        <Icon name="solar:global-linear" class="w-5 h-5" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>